RELATIONS
  View or set diplomatic relations with other countries.

SYNTAX
  relations [<cnum>]
  rela      [<cnum>]

DESCRIPTION
  Shows your current diplomatic stance toward other nations, or
  sets it when given a target country.

  Relation levels (from most hostile to most friendly):
    AT_WAR      - you are at war.  Units may attack freely
    HOSTILE     - hostile but no declared war
    NEUTRAL     - neither friendly nor hostile (default)
    FRIENDLY    - friendly, limited cooperation
    ALLIED      - allied, full cooperation and intelligence sharing

  With no argument, shows your relations with all countries.
  With a country number, shows your relation with that country.

  To change relations, use 'info declare'.

EXAMPLE
  relations                 see all your diplomatic stances
  relations 3               see your stance toward country 3

SEE ALSO
  declare  nation  power  report  telegram
